<sect1 id="zend.locale.appendix.numberscripts">

    <title>Supported number notations in Zend_Locale_Format::toNumberSystem()</title>

    <para>
        <code>Zend_Locale_Format::toNumberSystem()</code> converts digits between different <ulink url="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Arabic_numerals">numeral systems</ulink>.
    </para>

